# Electron and electron-builder both default to canonical GitHub URLs
# in their current versions, so no project-level mirror config is needed.
# To override (e.g. corporate proxy), set these env vars instead — the
# unprefixed .npmrc package configs are deprecated and emit warnings:
#   ELECTRON_MIRROR=https://your.mirror/
#   ELECTRON_BUILDER_BINARIES_MIRROR=https://your.mirror/
